children.name: attribute
children.description: Generic entity metadata attributes of the user.

children.name: first_name
children.description: First name of the user (for example, 'John').

children.name: first_seen_time
children.description: The first observed time for a user. The value is calculated on the basis of the first time the identifier was observed.

children.name: group_identifiers
children.description: Product object identifiers of the group(s) the user belongs to. A vendor-specific identifier to uniquely identify the group(s) the user belongs to (a GUID, LDAP OID, or similar).

children.name: groupid
children.description: The ID of the group that the user belongs to. Deprecated in favor of the repeated group_identifiers field.

children.name: last_bad_password_attempt_time
children.description: User last bad password attempt timestamp.

children.name: last_name
children.description: Last name of the user (for example, 'Locke').

children.name: product_object_id
children.description: A vendor-specific identifier to uniquely identify the entity (for example, a GUID, LDAP OID, or similar).

children.name: role_description
children.description: System role description for user. Deprecated: use attribute.roles.

children.name: role_name
children.description: System role name for user. Deprecated: use attribute.roles.

children.name: time_off
children.description: User time off leaves from active work.

children.name: user_authentication_status
children.description: Authentication status, can be used to describe the status of authentication for a user or particular credential.

children.name: user_display_name
children.description: The display name of the user (for example, 'John Locke').

children.name: windows_sid
children.description: The Microsoft Windows SID of the user.
